                    "description": "Within the TechMed Centre and the Faculty of Science and Technology of the University of Twente, I am responsible for the shared infrastructure of our Health domain, which consists of various cell biology labs, our animal facility and, primarily, the simulation centre. \n\nAs department head, I am responsible for the day to day operations of our expansive simulation centre (formerly known as ECTM), investment decisions and policy development for optimal usage of our facilities by our educational programmes, research groups and various external parties.\n\nCurrently, I am coordinating the development of our new simulation centre and medical research labs, which will be opened in Fall 2019.",
